column1: Noise columns C-F are % normalized to White - Black (1.45 density range = 244.8 pxls).  Columns M-P are % normalized to max pixel level.
A-noise and A-fstop (cols K-L) are mean of RBGY channels.
S/N (signal/noise) and SNR(dB) (20*log10(signal/noise)) for the 6 gray patches.  A is Average of RBGY channels.
